data.name: ReadChildCareTaxCreditFactors
data.value: select IDENTIFIER, EXPIRATION_DATE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, ADJ_GROSS_INC_MAX, ADJ_GROSS_INC_MIN, KS_TAX_CR_PERCENT, FED_TAX_CR_PERCENT, MAX_MTHLY_CR_MCH, MAX_MTHLY_CR_1_CH, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST from CKT_CHLD_CTC_FCTRS where (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (EXPIRATION_DATE > @effectiveDate) order by ADJ_GROSS_INC_MIN
